Any updates on this topic? I'm stuck in the same issue :(

---

UPDATE after quick experiments:

changing 'null'

```typescript
@Column('enum', { enum: StructuralNode, nullable: true, default: null})
public structuralNode: StructuralNode;
```
to 'undefined' seems to work in my case :)

```typescript
@Column('enum', { enum: StructuralNode, nullable: true, default: undefined })
public structuralNode: StructuralNode;
```
